# Critical extraction note: hiq uses **Hare `...`
# variadic-spread for spec passing** at hiq/main.
# ha:41 — `getopt::parse(os::args, usage...)`
# spreads the `usage` array into variadic args.
# Hare's `...` is the ARRAY-TO-VARIADIC SPREAD
# OPERATOR (post-fix on the array).  Sister to
